    "summary": "In this transcript, the user presents symptoms of a possible eye infection (redness, pain, yellow discharge) and asks for self-treatment advice. The assistant diagnoses the condition as potentially bacterial/conjunctivitis and confidently prescribes a specific medication regimen (OTC drops and ointment) with exact dosing intervals, while simultaneously advising on oral painkiller compatibility.",
